{"tid":2505823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那次貸危機] 深房理事件","createTime":"2021-04-27T02:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T06:55:46.000Z","uid":207767,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"718a1aea5d0a1fda6cf3504dbbe355f3308fd5ec","tid":2505823,"uid":207767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"sorry for 殘體，圖片太長，所以用埋加密，請使用以瀏覽器開啟閱讀圖片<br />\n<br />\n今鋪支那自己有人想發圍，玩緊美國08年類似既次貸，如果一爆，深圳樓價超越香港100倍不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot; <strong> 深房理團隊主要採取批量購房的方式，一群人把小區的所有筍盤拿下，人為製造房源稀缺性，市場上沒有高性價比房源，真正的剛需客戶就只能高價買單了。他們只集中推薦和購買某些熱門樓盤，會員間互相拉抬價格，不斷以更高的價格接盤幾個特定的小區，人為拔高小區成交價。</strong><br />\n<br />\n深房理在資金操作上，在法律上做了&ldquo;聰明&rdquo;的隔離設計，先不細說。<br />\n<br />\n但深房理的炒作手段，並不是首創。通過集資手段，將募集來資金投入到房地產中，並通過合約來管理，這種操作方法在海外被稱作&ldquo;REITs&rdquo;。在美國是很成熟的一種投資手段，已經有幾十年曆史並有嚴格的監管法規。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但係支那冇人管啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdjPiENNfkXeCttW9wXzeXLpcv31BnqvMGYuZ4QP2LqNB?filename=pBo8u24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBo8u24.jpg&h=bb4f8152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解深圳最近有咁撚多官辭職，都係因為哩一單野，中央都唔敢咁玩，但下面d人就當睇唔到，祝佢地早日支爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba7b8e0974b55050f2f2fbcf293e2004f0ccd7c","tid":2505823,"uid":207767,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUDKTcWJ2sdZu5PHC9kZfN6iiErs7VPQrpKFpWxMGacsq?filename=9LvrgKB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LvrgKB.jpg&h=1e74af19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR45wx8J9zGG6Q9n6FBb25bqmanUPBtRJPCtHwhj3t4fG?filename=JVdsLCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVdsLCX.jpg&h=c6912204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中一個走佬既官，明顯黨中央叫佢地自我搜查個時有隱瞞好多野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8499c4e33b370cb5759060f8273cee28960cc850","tid":2505823,"uid":207767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmenPie5DxzKq5YGWz3uVvVoyD1H15dePDNczKdjQMLHKr?filename=bkuvJp0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkuvJp0.jpg&h=87bff334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcmuVthkWJfdTg4HQwQh1fA8enSZV8YdK3kvLQwnTSRZZ?filename=5Ws9ewG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ws9ewG.jpg&h=8e952369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資本主義其實並未真正理解資本主義的極致意義，而支那特色社會主義領悟到了"},{"pid":"fa68f5acec38c5739b0b9718d490e878d86094c1","tid":2505823,"uid":207767,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:08:17.000Z","msg":"支那國務院2020年737號國務院令《防範和處置非法集資條例》2021年5月1日起，因非法投資受到損失，由集資參與人自行承擔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWvw3xqr4GvEV2h7TBQfCV1zDZhG9YedPdcQZPy7qTC28?filename=KJ5yGck.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJ5yGck.png&h=3c9cb760&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7f5f91d44d657a2b7cff6882db85e29b0f4e7cd","tid":2505823,"uid":207767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVJzowgT3Vqe6WDjPFGCp5Ynb1JbwuKJX7n7VrixU7K5j?filename=Bd3Hzyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBd3Hzyd.jpg&h=ddd5e58c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPytEFCbbuQMYQDUBxK87K28arwXvzKL6uhxXNCgsZqyd?filename=17yz96z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17yz96z.jpg&h=485ed68d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行深圳中心支行最新公佈的數據顯示：在2021年3月份，可能有超過2000億的&ldquo;熱錢&rdquo;撤離了深圳。<br />\n<br />\n可以作為佐證的依據是，對比中國人民銀行深圳支行3月末和2月末的深圳市本外幣各項存款餘額的差額，可以發現，3月末，深圳市本外幣各項存款餘額103551.04億元，同比增長15.1％，比2月末的深圳市本外幣各項存款餘額105442.22億元少了1891億元。<br />\n<br />\n而在此之前深圳基本上每個月會新增資金1000億到2000億元。以此，有媒體認為，3月份，保守估計，深圳有2000多億熱錢撤離深圳。<br />\n<br />\n深圳特區超越香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a27ebafbffb7a7d33570c0c40ad0f57f0571160","tid":2505823,"uid":139863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"而家俾中央stop咗?<br />\n定係繼續run緊?"},{"pid":"1f2827d5f067c4c8bd39fb03645c779ed56f9c7d","tid":2505823,"uid":207767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9a27ebafbffb7a7d33570c0c40ad0f57f0571160","tid":2505823,"uid":139863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"而家俾中央stop咗?<br />\n定係繼續run緊?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"中央好似話有公佈政策，但實際點樣？我都係估佢凍結銀行資金&amp;回收佢地樓契。<br />\n<br />\n銀行暫停左相關人員既信貸囉，但外面有幾多人夾錢買左，就唔知了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f361351464f58188a6e74e937510e3006d966a1","tid":2505823,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a845925ca4b69b24321b72cf0b81aa133d833392","tid":2505823,"uid":170249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"唔怪得深圳樓價不斷升<br />\n<br />\n連我鄉下果邊啲新樓都可以破3萬人仔每平方米<br />\n<br />\n仲要唔俾原居民係自己地起樓 十年前開始不停打壓"},{"pid":"b32a4f350bf6424bfeba80286a761d795278479a","tid":2505823,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a27ebafbffb7a7d33570c0c40ad0f57f0571160","tid":2505823,"uid":139863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"而家俾中央stop咗?<br />\n定係繼續run緊?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"你慌佢唔會遍地開花，2000億熱錢離開深圳，我有其中100分之1，我都會諗不如自己做庄搞返一壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e92fc9516f8d1990b333b79598262a41902fbe","tid":2505823,"uid":207767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:30:19.000Z","msg":"自2020年4月開展經營貸專項整治以來，針對2020年初輿情反映深圳經營貸違規進入房地產領域的情況，深圳銀保監局第一時間明確監管要求並迅速部署轄內中資商業銀行，對15.4萬筆、1771.73億元經營貸業務進行了全面排查，選取6家銀行集中開展現場檢查，檢查覆蓋率近50%。針對發現的問題，責令銀行立查立改，提前收回21筆、5180萬元涉嫌違規貸款，叫停風險隱患較大的業務，處罰違規機構4家，處罰問責違規責任人14人次，處罰金額合計575萬元。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;也就是說，<span class=\"red\">在深圳1771.73億元的經營貸規模中，最終只發現了5180萬元涉嫌違規貸款 </span>，佔比僅為0.029%。而5180萬元在目前的深圳房地產市場上，按照70%的貸款比例計算僅僅只能買3套房。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">DLLM，1770億你凍結得5180萬，剩低個d又俾深圳高官吞左？</span>"},{"pid":"8da783418ea72be407065e6a52e27f628b6d16c8","tid":2505823,"uid":207767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYmz7ANqhHTeRzjJrCqcb8cq5w7MA2T6aHFyvhBtukACD?filename=COQrgTv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOQrgTv.jpg&h=85b14859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTRtPEdnB6L34kYjBYFKzY8G2kehShHiPqunFNhfvExjx?filename=id4jBTw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fid4jBTw.jpg&h=0f4fe8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbAAeZcjDg812yZmNJk2DzFJMQ9eynsSBp1XyTQzuJp6R?filename=WH5ZBTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWH5ZBTx.jpg&h=2c291e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲古惑過香港嗰啲aa"},{"pid":"bdc6a5480ddca1698af9b22d026c819d5e1e9071","tid":2505823,"uid":2